NUMBER 2242
NAME Wild Forest
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
The devastating destruction that raged through the home seems to have 
originated here. A huge crater has carved out a gaping hole in the floor
of the forest, filled now with the snows of winter. The stream flows down 
from the north, chill with chunks of snow and ice. The crevice to the dens is 
decorated by icicles, and the opening leading down to the meadow is 
tramped down by the passage of many paws.
*DESCRIPTION_END
