NUMBER 2243
NAME Forest, Clearing
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
The meadow is snowy, yet full of life, and the large pool of water is clean
and healthy looking. Ice covers over a small pool of water. The dam is 
covered with winter's thick blanket. The trees nearby shelter part
of the area from the icy winds. The debris pile still remains, but it seems 
almost natural to the area.
*DESCRIPTION_END
