IFENTRY -1
 IFVAR INTNUM6 = 5
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 45
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER An elder wolf bounds down to the ground in front of you.
  ECHO OTHERS An elder wolf bounds down to the ground in front of %n.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf sniffs you.
  ECHO OTHERS The elder wolf sniffs %n and seems to speak to %i quietly.
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf growls, "Greetings, youngling."
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf growls, "I see it is time for you to venture into the outside world, to make an adult of yourself."
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf growls, "But first, you must know more of who your people are, so that you do not lose your sense of what you are, out there, amongst the others."
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf growls, "You are a wolfling, you must never forget that. Please, assume your wolf form and remain that way until we finish. [Type: TRANSFORM]"
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf growls, "Shemri created our kind as defense against the darker and less evolved lycanthrope population of this world."
  PLREVENT 2 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The elder wolf gestures towards a dark opening in the cliffside.
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf growls, "Beyond this opening lies the cave of smoke..."
  PLREVENT 2 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf growls, "While you are in the cave, let the scent of the sacred smoke cleanse your spirit."
  PLREVENT 2 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf growls, "Breath deeply my child. Enter the cave and discover your mind."
  PLREVENT 2 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The elder wolf looks at you speculatively for a moment and then, with a look of approval, bounds off into the boulders above.
  ECHO OTHERS The elder wolf looks at %n speculatively for a moment and then, with a look of approval, bounds off into the boulders above.
  EQUAL INTNUM6 6
 ENDIF
ENDIF
